#: translations/abilities.merged.md:141
msgid ""
"## Spellcasting Ability Bards, paladins, sorcerers, and warlocks use "
"Charisma as their spellcasting ability, which helps determine the saving "
"throw DCs of spells they cast."
msgstr ""

