#. type: Plain text
#: translations/abilities.merged.md:150
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"## Constitution Checks \n"
"Constitution checks are uncommon, and no skills apply to Constitution "
"checks, because the endurance this ability represents is largely passive "
"rather than involving a specific effort on the part of a character or "
"monster. A Constitution check can model your attempt to push beyond normal "
"limits, however.    \n"
"The GM might call for a Constitution check when you try to accomplish tasks "
"like the following: \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '* '
#: translations/abilities.merged.md:156
msgid "Hold your breath"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '* '
#: translations/abilities.merged.md:156
